decision_details:
- The proposal made by the Minister of Finance to present the following Gazette Notifications which include the Orders published under the Special Commodity Levy Act, No.48 of 2007 with a view to stabilizing the market price, providing relief to the consumers and protecting the local agriculture, in Parliament for approval.

(i)	Gazette Extraordinary Notification No.2236/66 dated 2021‑07‑18; 

(ii)	Gazette Extraordinary Notification No.2240/20 dated 2021‑08‑11; 

(iii)	Gazette Extraordinary Notification No.2244/8 dated 2021-09‑07; 

(iv)	Gazette Extraordinary Notification No.2249/3 dated 2021‑10‑11; 

(v)	Gazette Extraordinary Notification No.2249/16 dated 2021‑10‑13; 

(vi)	Gazette Extraordinary Notification No.2252/9 dated 2021‑11‑02; and

(vii)	Gazette Extraordinary Notification No.2252/25 dated 	2021‑11‑02.
